hoia.me: Estonia's new mobile application helps to quickly identify possible close contacts with COVID-19 infected individuals. Download the app here:
allVaccinatedPercentage: Total vaccinated out of entire population
completelyVaccinatedFromTotalVaccinatedP: Fully vaccinated out of total vaccinated
disclaimerNavbar: All data shown in this application presents the date the test was confirmed. Data shows results up until 7am of the current day.
distributionOfAgeSexTests: Distribution of tests by age and sex
genderChart: Positive and negative tests by sex
testsPer10000: Positive tests per 10,000 population by county
navbarDescription: Statistics about COVID-19 disease caused by coronavirus spread in Estonia. The application is being maintained by OKEE in collaboration with Terviseamet
positiveNegativeTitle: Positive and negative tests by county (%)
